{"title":"姐姐回家了","authors":["曹纬"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":8,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐姐回家了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹纬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天姐姐从镇上回到家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一个工人陪着她。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敢说我认得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个开拖拉机的叔叔就是他！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年他曾给我们耕过地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前两个月又来帮我们社里收庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也就是他那一次来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的姐姐才离开了家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他这个人可真好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难怪妈妈常夸他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他现在还是个老师呢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说教姐姐开拖拉机的就是他。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可真怪，今天他来了直叫“妈？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈也叫我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“快去打盆水，让哥哥先洗脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后再到园里把菜拔。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁他没注意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我轻轻拉拉妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“昨天我还喊他叔叔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天他怎么叫你妈？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈只是笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑得不说话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看看姐姐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的脸象院里的石榴花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把我往怀里紧紧抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头抿嘴笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又轻轻把我骂："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“淘气的小妮子你懂啥！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}